FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773666674
OL,3,CFamily 'extremely worried' after 77-
OL,4,Cyear-old man missing for 10 days
OL,6,F"The family are extremely worried
OL,7,Fabout him and I'd urge anyone who may
OL,8,Fhave seen him, or has any information
OL,9,Fabout his whereabouts, to come forward.
OL,11,F"These last couple of weeks have been
OL,12,Fvery difficult for us as we struggle
OL,13,Fto understand where Graham may have
OL,14,Fgone.
OL,16,F"If you are reading this, Graham,
OL,17,Fplease call and let us know that you
OL,18,Fare safe."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@JO]
