FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773666674
OL,3,CFamily 'extremely worried' after 77-
OL,4,Cyear-old man missing for 10 days
OL,6,FGloucestershire Police says extensive
OL,7,Fsearches have taken place, and
OL,8,Fofficers with specialist search
OL,9,Ftraining have been conducting house to
OL,10,Fhouse enquiries, searches on the
OL,11,Fground and reviewing CCTV.
OL,13,FThere has also been support from the
OL,14,FSevern Area Rescue Association and
OL,15,FSouth West England Rescue Association.
OL,17,FThe force added that numerous
OL,18,Fpotential sightings have been reported
OL,19,Fto police, and officers are continuing
OL,20,Fto work through these, but so far none
OL,21,Fare confirmed to have been Graham.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
