FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773666674
OL,3,CFamily 'extremely worried' after 77-
OL,4,Cyear-old man missing for 10 days
OL,6,FGraham is keen walker and has been
OL,7,Fknown to walk long distances in the
OL,8,Fpast.
OL,10,FHe is described as being around 5ft
OL,11,F8ins tall, is of a slim build and is
OL,12,Fbald. He also wears glasses and walks
OL,13,Fwith a slight shuffle.
OL,15,FIt is believed Graham will now be
OL,16,Fwearing different clothes to the ones
OL,17,Fhe was wearing in the images shared by
OL,18,Fthe police as they have since been
OL,19,Ffound at his home address.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
